   Visitor and Student Visas (US Dept of State)
   http://travel.state.gov/visa_services.html#niv
   This State Department site gives information on how to apply for
   visitor and student visas. Find out about the application process and
   important information you need to know before you apply. An important
   resource for international students.
   Related Topics: International students  Trip planning
   __________________________________________________________________


