   EducationUSA (US State Dept)
   http://exchanges.state.gov/education/educationusa/aboutasa.htm
   The Education and Information Resources Branch promotes the
   international exchange of students and scholars by providing support
   for a network of over 400 educational advising centers worldwide.
   Locate the center nearest you! Valuable resource.
   Related Topics: International students

